            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-description field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><p>A truly unique space to pursue your talents and artistic aspirations.</p>
<h3>Rent a studio</h3>
<p>The Nepean Creative Arts Centre's arts-specific studios are available for rent, including:</p>
<ul>
<li>Specialized studios equipped for visual and performing arts.</li>
<li>Dance studios with sprung floors, barres and floor-to-ceiling mirrors.&nbsp;</li>
<li>Soundproofed music studios,</li>
<li>Black box theatre,</li>
<li>Recital hall,</li>
<li>Set construction workshop,</li>
<li>Meeting rooms.</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="https://forms.ottawa.ca/en/form/rcfs/parks-facilities/room-rental-form?roomName=Dance%20Studio%201%20-%20Nepean%20Creative%20Arts%20Centre&amp;facilityEmail=ncac.cacn%40ottawa.ca">Room rental form</a></p>
