            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item"><h3>About</h3>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>Home to the following groups offering a variety of programs and events: </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://cccaa.ca/">Canada-China Culture and Art Association</a></li>
<li><a href="https://canadianshowtimechorus.com/">Canadian Showtime Chorus</a></li>
<li><a href="https://capitalcircus.ca/">Capital Circus School</a></li>
<li>Children's Chinese Dance</li>
<li>Eastern Original Art</li>
<li><a href="https://www.taoist.org/locations/ottawa-west/">Fung Loy Kok Institute of Taoism Tai Chi</a></li>
<li><a href="http://gharana.ca/">Gharana Arts</a></li>
<li>Kalinka</li>
<li><a href="https://www.kanatasymphony.ca/">Kanata Symphony Orchestra</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.lakesideplayers.com/">Lakeside Players</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.lespetitsballets.com/">Les Petits Ballets</a></li>
<li>Natwari Arts</li>
<li><a href="https://nepeanconcertband.com/">Nepean Concert Band</a></li>
<li><a href="https://odysseyshowcase.org/">Odyssey Showcase</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.kingdomtheatre.ca/">Once Upon a Kingdom</a></li>
<li><a href="https://orientaldancetroupe.ca/">Oriental Dance Troupe of Ottawa</a></li>
<li>Ottawa Chinese Arts Centre</li>
<li><a href="https://www.ottawagatineauprintmakers.ca/">Ottawa-Gatineau Printmakers Connective</a></li>
<li>Ottawa Valley Decorative Artists</li>
<li><a href="https://owcarvers.com/index.html">Outaouais Woodcarvers</a></li>
<li>Panharmonic Steel Drum Band</li>
<li><a href="https://www.phoenixplayers.ca/">Phoenix Players</a></li>
<li>Rathi School of Dance</li>
<li><a href="https://schoolofmoderndance.com/">The School of Modern Dance</a></li>
<li>Spanish Folk Dance Troupe of Ottawa</li>
<li><a href="https://www.suzart.ca/">Suzart</a></li>
<li>Sweet Homeland Association</li>
</ul>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>Our sister facility -&nbsp;The&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><a href="https://ottawa.ca/en/recreation-and-parks/recreation-facilities/facility-listing/nepean-visual-arts-centre"><span><span><span>Nepean Visual Arts Centre</span></span></span></a></span><span><span><span>&nbsp;offers </span></span></span><span><span><span><span>specialty arts classes taught by accomplished artists - painters, potters, illustrators, sculptors, photographers - in custom studio spaces for participants of all levels of ability.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
